
ca_key_gen.py - produce all keys 
 
1. public key of ca is in 'ca_pubkey_dir.txt'

2. private key of user1 - u1_privkey_dir.txt

3. private key of user2 - u2_privkey_dir.txt

4. public keys of user1 and user2 - user_pubkey_dir.txt


############################################################################################

sender_encryption.py - produce encrypted text for user2(receiver)


encrypted text written in - sender_encryp_msg_dir.txt


############################################################################################

receiver_decryption.py - produce decrypted  text 

final obtained decrypted text written in - original_msg_by_vig_dec_dir.txt